        take, especially those, like blood<br>
        thinners, that affect blood clotting. One<br>
        week before the surgery, you will have<br>
        to stop taking aspirin, ibuprofen, and<br>
        anticoagulants. You will also have a<br>
        chest x-ray. <br>
